---
// How It Works Section Component
// Explains the password generation process and security
---

<section
  id="how-it-works"
  class="py-20 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900"
  aria-labelledby="how-it-works-heading"
>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2
        id="how-it-works-heading"
        class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4"
      >
        How It Works
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Understanding the secure password generation process and why your data stays private
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Process Steps -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-16">
      <!-- Left Column: Steps -->
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div class="flex items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-lg mr-4">
            1
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">
              Configure Your Preferences
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              Choose your desired password length (4-128 characters) and select which character 
              types to include: uppercase letters, numbers, and special symbols. Your preferences 
              are applied instantly without any server communication.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div class="flex items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 to-green-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-lg mr-4">
            2
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">
              Cryptographic Random Generation
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              Our generator uses the <strong>Web Crypto API</strong> to create truly random numbers 
              with maximum entropy. This ensures each password is unpredictable and secure against 
              brute-force attacks, far superior to standard pseudo-random generators.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div class="flex items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-purple-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-lg mr-4">
            3
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">
              Local Processing & Validation
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              The password is generated entirely in your browser's memory. We ensure it meets 
              your criteria by including at least one character from each selected type, then 
              shuffle the result for additional security.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 4 -->
        <div class="flex items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500 to-orange-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-lg mr-4">
            4
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">
              Instant Analysis & Copy
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              Get real-time strength analysis with crack time estimates and security feedback. 
              Copy your password to the clipboard with one click using secure browser APIs. 
              Everything happens locally—no data ever leaves your device.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column: Visual -->
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-8 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
          <!-- Browser Window Mockup -->
          <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
            <div class="flex space-x-2">
              <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-red-400 rounded-full"></div>
              <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-yellow-400 rounded-full"></div>
              <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-green-400 rounded-full"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-4 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Your Browser</div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Process Flow -->
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-center p-3 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 rounded-lg">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6V4m0 2a2 2 0 100 4m0-4a2 2 0 110 4m-6 8a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 100 4m0-4v2m0-6V4m6 6v10m6-2a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 100 4m0-4v2m0-6V4"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Configure Options</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gray-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-center p-3 bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/20 rounded-lg">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Web Crypto API</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gray-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-center p-3 bg-purple-50 dark:bg-purple-900/20 rounded-lg">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-purple-600 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 3v2m6-2v2M9 19v2m6-2v2M5 9H3m2 6H3m18-6h-2m2 6h-2M7 19h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2zM9 9h6v6H9V9z"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Local Processing</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gray-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-center p-3 bg-orange-50 dark:bg-orange-900/20 rounded-lg">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-600 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 7a2 2 0 012 2m4 0a6 6 0 01-7.743 5.743L11 17H9v2H7v2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1v-2.586a1 1 0 01.293-.707l5.964-5.964A6 6 0 1121 9z"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Secure Password Ready</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- No Server Communication -->
          <div class="mt-6 p-3 bg-red-50 dark:bg-red-900/20 rounded-lg border-2 border-dashed border-red-200 dark:border-red-800">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M18.364 18.364A9 9 0 005.636 5.636m12.728 12.728L5.636 5.636m12.728 12.728L18.364 5.636M5.636 18.364l12.728-12.728"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-red-700 dark:text-red-300">No Server Communication</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Security Highlights -->
    <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6 text-center">
        Why This Approach Is Secure
      </h3>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Security Point 1 -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 to-green-600 rounded-full mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">
            Zero Data Transmission
          </h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Your passwords never leave your device. No network requests, no server logs, 
            no data collection—complete privacy guaranteed.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Security Point 2 -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-blue-600 rounded-full mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">
            Cryptographic Randomness
          </h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Uses browser's Web Crypto API for true random number generation, 
            providing maximum entropy and unpredictability.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Security Point 3 -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-purple-600 rounded-full mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9v-9m0-9v9"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">
            Open Source Transparency
          </h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            All code is open and auditable. No hidden functionality, 
            no backdoors—you can verify exactly how your passwords are generated.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Technical Details -->
    <div class="mt-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-50 to-gray-100 dark:from-gray-800 dark:to-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">
      <details class="group">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer list-none">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
            Technical Implementation Details
          </h4>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 text-sm">
            <div>
              <h5 class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Random Number Generation</h5>
              <ul class="space-y-1 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                <li>• Uses <code class="bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-600 px-1 rounded">crypto.getRandomValues()</code></li>
                <li>• Fallback to <code class="bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-600 px-1 rounded">Math.random()</code> if unavailable</li>
                <li>• Ensures uniform distribution across character sets</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h5 class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Security Measures</h5>
              <ul class="space-y-1 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                <li>• Fisher-Yates shuffle algorithm</li>
                <li>• Character type validation</li>
                <li>• Pattern detection and avoidance</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>